<paragraph blockId="11.[810,1420,1928,2091]" pageId="11" pageNumber="518">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[810,972,1967,1991]" pageId="11" pageNumber="518">Identification.</emphasis>
Small prostrate herb, cylindrical stem very branched. Differentiated by its alternate to sub-op- posite, sessile or sub-sessile, elliptic-ovate leaves with mucronulate apex, 
<quantity box="[1014,1121,2067,2091]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.25" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="3.5" pageId="11" pageNumber="518" unit="mm" value="5.25" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="3.5">3.5–7 mm</quantity>
length and 
<quantity box="[1247,1354,2067,2091]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.25" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="11" pageNumber="518" unit="mm" value="3.25" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="1.5">1.5–5 mm</quantity>
wide.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[810,1420,160,218]" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">
species. Considered Presumably Extinct in 
<collectingRegion country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">São Paulo state</collectingRegion>
, and Endangered in 
<collectingCountry box="[1082,1152,194,218]" name="Brazil" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[810,1420,234,434]" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[810,997,234,258]" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">Brazilian range.</emphasis>
South (
<collectingRegion box="[1080,1171,234,258]" country="Brazil" name="Para" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">PR state</collectingRegion>
) and Southeast (except ES and RJ states) regions.
</paragraph>
