<paragraph blockId="12.[167,778,1294,1458]" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[168,279,1295,1319]" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">Remarks.</emphasis>
An unusual species, observed in low frequency in the PEJY grasslands and commonly occurring in clusters with other individuals from the same species. Considered Presumably Extinct in 
<collectingRegion box="[558,729,1399,1423]" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">São Paulo state</collectingRegion>
and Near Threatened in 
<collectingCountry box="[384,454,1434,1458]" name="Brazil" pageId="12" pageNumber="519">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
